      "content": "honestly he's like 75 and he's always been a bit slow with his words when he's tired, so he's being really stubborn about it. he's even saying he feels a bit dizzy but thinks it's just the jet lag hitting him. you really think it's an emergency? couldn't it just be dehydration or him being really worn out from the 14 hour flight?",
